name: FOLLOW-002
description:
Missed doing this thing, yep, the drawing and also the upside down walking.

Welcome to the 'FOLLOW' Series

In every phase of life, we're following something or someone, but does that mean they're ahead of us? I hate to break it to you but we're in an endless loop. Who you follow, prolly following someone too! Be you! Take the lead.

--------------------

Collecting this and other works by Jakestudyos means supporting a dream of the artist to continue his craft while making a living.
Join Jakestudyos on his journey and evolution.
